---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="py-24">
    <h1 class="mb-6 font-serif text-6xl text-white">
      Selected Works
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-2xl text-neutral">
      Desired feeling

      The recruiter should think:
      
      "Okay, there's substance behind all this."
      
      Then:
      
      "They've actually done the work."
      
      Then:
      
      "I can see evidence of product judgment."
       
      Design implication

      Most structured page.
      
      Most product-like page.
      
      Most scannable page.
      
      The recruiter is evaluating.
      
      Not exploring.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>